ygData.messageBody:
For those who are interested, there is going to be an informal EQ get
together in Aurora (a suburb of Denver CO) on October the 24th at 1pm. I'm
not sure at this point how many people will be there, but we hope to have a
good showing. We also hope to be announcing/discussing an EQ convention for
early next year! I know for sure that we will havwe people from several
different servers and at least 4 bards so far.

The Place: Attactix Game Store
15107 E Hampden Ave
Aurora CO 80014
(303) 699-3349
ask for Heather (Sol Ro, E'ci) Dean (E'ci,test),
Walter (Sol Ro), or Ted (Sol Ro)

The Time: October 24th
1PM - ???
No alcoholic beverages allowed
(Continuance of the gathering amongst the adults to a place
with alcoholic beverages is expected to occur)

Let all your friends who might be interested know. For further info contact
Heather at herefew@... or myself at dean_kimes@...

Hope to see some of you there!
